nodes.text: Doro was a male member of the Garos Underground during the early years of the New Republic. Born in 22 BBY, Doro was twenty-eight years old by 6 ABY. While on a mission with Alexandra Winger, their cover was blown by Imperial scout troopers and during their flight from the Empire, Doro was struck by a blaster bolt. The blast did not kill him, but the resulting fall cracked his head on a rock, killing him.
